sql: SELECT COUNT(CASE WHEN booking_status='IssuedBusiness' THEN 1 END) as bookings FROM sme_analytics.sme_leadbookingrevenue WHERE bookingdate >= DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE) AND paymentstatus = 300 AND mkt_category IN ('SEO')
explanation: Metric: bookings; Time: this month; Filter mkt_category in ['SEO']; Online payments only (paymentstatus=300)
